:::Cyclonus/Hun-Grr:::

::Cyclonus nods and walks to the Terrorcons.  He sees Sinnertwin, 
Rippersnapper, and Hun-Grr. he looks to Hun-Grr::
Cyclonus: Hun-Grr, where are Cutthroat and Blot?
Hun-Grr: Hun-grr on comm with Blot, dont know where Cutthroat is.  BLOT, QUIT 
GUARDING SLAGGING CAVE AND GET OVER HERE!
::He then opens his comm to Cutthroat::
Hun-Grr: Cutthroat, come to Hun-Grr's position, Cyclonus want us.
Cyclonus: When you get your team together, go to Megatron.
::Cyclonus then finds the Bodicons::
Cyclonus: Alright guys, report to Megatrons position, he needs you for a 
mission.
